  id: 8
  title: Investment Strategies
  description: 'You find yourself surrounded by a group of older men in suits.


    They''re
    in town on business and were amused by your performance. The conversation drags
    on as the men brag about the money they''ve made over the years.


    Eventually,
    one of the men turns to you and asks, "So what is your plan for building capital?"'
  options:
  - title: Short-term gains
    description: <color=green>+$1</color> commission
    requirement: 
    conclusion: 'The younger executive types agree with you and recount their latest
      cost cutting measures. '
    isHidden: 0
    item: {fileID: 0}
    consumable: {fileID: 0}
    tag: 
  - title: Long-term investments
    description: <color=green>+$3</color> interest cap
    requirement: 
    conclusion: 'The older men look pleased as you talk about how your current investments
      of growing. '
    isHidden: 0
    item: {fileID: 0}
    consumable: {fileID: 0}
    tag: 
  - title: Capital requires the exploitation of labor
    description: <color=purple>+2</color> arrogance
    requirement: 
    conclusion: 'The businessmen look genuinely annoyed, but who better to annoy?


      You
      know capitalism is the problem. '
